article_title: Meet The Man Who Might Just Save Obamacare From Collapsing

article_metadata.description: No one wins popularity points by defending health insurance companies or their handsomely paid executives. But the bottom line is, when insurance companies lose money, they raise the rates for health insurance coverage.
article_metadata.author: Jeff Smedsrud
